      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/388317a8-538d-11e3-8123-52540035b04c).  Ran 19 tests.  No failures.",
