      },
      "date": "2013-11-23 10:52:13.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/12157de8-5420-11e3-8c97-52540035b04c).  Ran 23 tests.  4 tests failed: insanity, conf-sanity, replay-single, sanity.",
