    {
      "id": "7c0ae869a93d5e8a1f0fecc8e371026c98c2ff01",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 117,
        "name": "Andreas Dilger",
        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2013-11-25 06:52:56.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nI'm not sure I understand why the agent inode should be skipped during scrub?  This is the only way for a remote direntry to get its FID back after backup/restore. The agent inode should have a valid LMA with the remote FID in it.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "5e8451cb86e75195f950eae442ce193bc4ef7e10",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 3,
        "name": "Fan Yong",
        "email": "fan.yong@intel.com",
        "username": "nasf",
        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2013-11-25 09:20:37.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nThe agent inode has FID-in-LMA, but it has no FID-in-OI. So when OI scrub found agent inode, it thought that the OI files have been removed and recreated. But it fact, it is not such case.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "9d0f3b5a52d24d4cc4ec56a51b02610cc282a751",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 117,
        "name": "Andreas Dilger",
        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2013-11-25 17:52:02.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Looks good to me, but someone else must approve\n\nI should have looked at the patch more closely. It seems to only be skipping the OI check, but is still being handled by the other LFSCK checks.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "6c67d1064eb5e30830ad01050ec60c07bbacdc1d",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 3,
        "name": "Fan Yong",
        "email": "fan.yong@intel.com",
        "username": "nasf",
        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2013-11-26 00:20:23.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nThe other OI scrub will skip it because of the \"LMAI_AGENT\" flag in LMA.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
